{"tid":1368322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"告警察 你們即將成為棄子","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:17:47.000Z","uid":48521,"like":212,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2569a4e67f104fa45de576f1822f3890ffbc8c29","tid":1368322,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"第一炮係由極建制同精打細算既香港總商會打起<br />\n如果無收到風 諗過度過既大商人會出黎呼籲成立獨立調查委員會 出黎損害自己牙力仲可能俾人秋後算帳嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二炮由政府第二把手政務司張建宗打出<br />\n知唔知點解 好多人都預測佐 拎警察祭旗會死為新特首施政蜜月期良藥<br />\n<br />\n林鄭下台 邊個會署理佢既職務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張建宗<br />\n<br />\n第三炮 由國防部話搞唔掂會出解放軍<br />\n你自己上場都知 用橡膠子彈市民根本都頂唔到<br />\n情報都應該知香港人最喜歡焦土<br />\n解放軍黎無任歡迎<br />\n點解唔用警察鎮壓要用有風險摧毀香港解放軍做同一樣野<br />\n<br />\n原來佢唔係同市民講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係同警察講唔好諗住政變呀 政變我出解放軍做番英明既中央政府</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你隻手仲乾淨 恭喜你 頂多一兩星期就搞掂<br />\n如果你洗濕曬個頭 我都恭喜你 洗定屎忽入去坐啦<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得自己仲有得救 收集到證據轉做污點證人可能都幫到你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有警察朋友就傳俾佢叫佢好自為之啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd7cddee0961a153423e10641c3461bfbacf8d4","tid":1368322,"uid":48521,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4899695457fa654e15be4bc74d0aa7db32426af7","tid":1368322,"uid":48521,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"Too long no one read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52b5995028e9d5a8b5a8235674c763475c9d8bd","tid":1368322,"uid":706,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"張建宗都出埋聲<br />\n到依家都仲未聞到垃圾桶味既真係死不足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過毅進仔無腦正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5bf304cae581c1cc1a01b4bb14cfeeefaf0eeb","tid":1368322,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"又會咁奇怪點咁咁多商家佬要講成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n[突發奇腸] 獨立調查委員會 可能唔係最好既方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqCfkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqCfkT</a>"},{"pid":"9a74a6bd054750474183bc7c94ee5376482eef42","tid":1368322,"uid":48521,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a52b5995028e9d5a8b5a8235674c763475c9d8bd","tid":1368322,"uid":706,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"張建宗都出埋聲<br />\n到依家都仲未聞到垃圾桶味既真係死不足惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過毅進仔無腦正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset